# Fal.ai API key — get one at https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your key. The key is used ONLY server-side
# (Vite dev middleware locally, Vercel serverless function in production); it is
# never bundled into the browser. Without it, image generation/editing falls back
# to the built-in simulation.
FAL_KEY=
